{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "搶奪目標", "storyInfo": "倫蒂尼姆城外，因陀羅與達格達對深池展開了一次突襲行動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$normal02_intro", "key": "$normal02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "7:25 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離倫蒂尼姆十公里，荒地車道"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 通訊信號消失前，黑鋼的飛行器就在前方一百米左右的位置。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等我用望遠鏡確定下具體方位——等等，你怎麼站起來了？！", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聞到煙味了沒？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沒......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下你手裡的鐵疙瘩吧，飛行器肯定就在前面。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不用先確認下敵人數量？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最多不超過三十個。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 呃，這也是你聞出來的？", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼亂七八糟的呢？出發之前，摩根跟我說了，他們小隊一般三十人一組。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哦，對，Misery傳回來的情報就是這麼說的。按照敵人的習慣，附近應該還有另外兩支小隊，他們之間會相互支援。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，他們還真把這裡當自家地盤了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你可別衝動。阿米婭說了，在進倫蒂尼姆之前，我們不能鬧出太大動靜，有那麼多勢力的眼睛盯著呢。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白輪，你在小兔子的隊裡，跟我們一塊行動幾天了？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 從離艦開始算，有五天了吧。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你知道從推進之王來到格拉斯哥幫，到她成為我的主子，一共花了多少時間？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......不知道。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩天。她只用了兩天。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一天，她打架贏了我。第二天，我們一塊打架贏了另一夥不懷好意的萊塔尼亞佬。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#10$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，我們就是過命的交情。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......雖說合作時間還不算長，但我很信任你的能力，因陀羅幹員。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。走吧，我們跟上達格達。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 達格達已經行動了？！你是說那道突然躥過去的黑影......", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛入夥的時候她還老惦記著什麼騎士架子，現在一有架打衝得比誰都快。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得跟緊一點，要不然架都被她一個人打完了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達出手精準，她一定會從飛行器的側面翻到頂上去。我們從背面繞，把周圍的人清一清，然後突擊飛行器的門。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 明白，我會給你打掩護。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹完這一架，你也是我們的好兄弟了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哈......哈哈。", "name": "羅德島幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按羅德島的規矩該怎麼說來著......想起來了。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救援目標，倫蒂尼姆市民一人，黑鋼駕駛員一人。敵方目標——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_012", "name2": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——深池。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_aircraft", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，坐規矩些，別想偷偷摸摸地碰發報機。", "name": "深池士兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別、別殺我！我只是手麻了，想稍微活動兩下......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你別使那麼大力氣，萬一真把這人弄死了，回去怎麼跟長官交代？", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 別忘了，我們的目標是這個人，弄走這台會飛的載具只是順便。", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你知道怎麼讓它動起來了？", "name": "深池士兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不知道。", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那你就不該一進來就把駕駛員弄死！依我看，還是別在這裡浪費時間了，把這人帶回去，這台飛不起來的破載具就留著吧。", "name": "深池士兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 外面這條路上都是我們的人，再待一會也沒什麼吧？薩卡茲在城內，大公爵的軍隊都駐紮在附屬地塊的軍營裡，不會有人來找我們麻煩。", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先、先生們，你們不是薩卡茲？", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你沒長眼睛嗎？我們怎麼可能會是那種髒東西！", "name": "深池士兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "髒、髒東西......呵呵......您說得對......", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 行了，除了問話以外，別跟這倫蒂尼姆人交談。這小子敢背叛薩卡茲，說不定有些來頭。", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也對，謹慎一點好。你動作快一點，我出去看看外面的人的情況。", "name": "深池士兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 剛才是不是有什麼動靜？", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，我的心跳聲音太大了......我什麼都聽不見。", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ventilatingduct_climb", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們被襲擊了？！頂上有東西——M-709，你在外面看到了嗎？M-709？！", "name": "深池士兵B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$indust_intro", "key": "$indust_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_doorclose", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 黑