 {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟個街頭混混似的？哈，眼神不錯。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  抓緊時間。這人不弱，比外面那些被你擊倒的都要強一些。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  能在薩卡茲和公爵部隊的夾縫中活動自如，甚至控制住了部分進出倫蒂尼姆的要道，深池並非散兵游勇。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我們需要儘快救出目標，回到安全區域。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了。“留給你們肆意妄為的時間不多了”，對吧？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想放狠話的話，這還不夠狠。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記不記得我怎麼教你的？應該說——", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想哭著求饒命的話，趁現在。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {