"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......白輪，麻煩隱蔽好自己。進來的敵人，我和因陀羅處理。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#7$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 他們在裡面！", "name": "深池士兵"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士們，救、救命！我可不想再落到他們手裡！", "name": "倫蒂尼姆市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，別出聲，躲裡面一點。", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#6$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達，我們只用帶回目標就行，對吧？那把這大鐵疙瘩拆了，應該也沒什麼問題？", "name": "因陀羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_155_tiger_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這話等回去以後，你跟推進之王說。", "name": "達格達"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_396_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}